"We have nothing to lose but our chains." @lateefahsimon #NI15
"Let's learn from one another. Let's take the lessons from our grandparents and great grandparents." @lateefahsimon #NI15
"As we innovate, you bring pies to your neighbors. Do you understand?" @lateefahsimon #NI15
"What is important for us is to make sure we know the land we're standing on, who our neighbors are, how we can collectively come together."
"How dare we take space if we're not ready to play?" @lateefahsimon #NI15
"This is the EMPIRE! Why are people dying on the streets? Why is our earth warming every single minute? We are smarter than this!" #NI15
"Too many people have stepped up for you to play small." @lateefahsimon #NI15
"Of course I'm going to run for office. Because failure's not an option - GAME ON!" @lateefahsimon #NI15
"When you tap out, where's the vision? Meet your goals. And then bring those folks along with you." @lateefahsimon #NI15
"Brothers and sisters, I want us to look intersectionally!" @lateefahsimon #NI15
"How dare I not look at the critical systems where we are NOT? ...I'm not going to lay it out on the field?" @lateefahsimon #NI15
"It was our vision to think big and that 'no' doesn't exist. That creating opportunities for our folks to win is the only option." #NI15
"Who's waiting for you? The people all over the globe. It's NEVER going to be the right time." @lateefahsimon #NI15
"I'm telling you, what are you WAITING for? If not you, WHO?" @lateefahsimon #NI15
"When we think about what's possible, I want us to think big." @lateefahsimon #NI15
"Altruism is not good enough because it doesn't change the systems. Go in, and go HARD!" @lateefahsimon #NI15
"Every single time you're told that it's actually okay to tap out, think about THIS moment! You don't have a choice." @lateefahsimon #NI15
"We have hungry people here in Seattle who are sleeping in the rain right now - these problems are BIG, but they're simple." @lateefahsimon

"We made a commitment to social justice so we left it ALL on the line." @lateefahsimon #NI15
"We can right the many wrongs in the world, and our impact can be truly significant. Game on!" @lateefahsimon #NI15
"We have been waiting for you. We've been WAITING for you." @lateefahsimon #NI15
